---
title: Tender Lamb Rump & Mushroom Red Wine Sauce with Dauphinoise Potatoes & Garlicky Green Beans
description: Lamb rump is usually served drizzled in a mint sauce, but we dare you to try out this mushroom gravy, decadent and rich in
earthy tones. Trust us, when it comes to lamb, a mushroom gravy is the new mint sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65bad65d03a5929119520374-e7786585.jpeg
